title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: When trying to export data from the attached report, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
OB: When attempting to export the data from the table, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
EB: The expected behavior is for the data to be exported successfully without any exceptions.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Open the attached report.  2. Attempt to export the data from the table.  The exception should be thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
